[
  {
    "startTime": 0.0,
    "endTime": 2.0,
    "text": "Mr. Dell won't be surprised to see us."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 2.0,
    "endTime": 4.0,
    "text": "Yeah, we might interrupt his third breakfast."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 5.0,
    "endTime": 10.0,
    "text": "Hey!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 10.0,
    "endTime": 12.0,
    "text": "Uh, hi, guys."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 12.0,
    "endTime": 12.0,
    "text": "What's up?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 12.0,
    "endTime": 13.0,
    "text": "School was canceled."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 13.0,
    "endTime": 14.0,
    "text": "What's that on your lips?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 14.0,
    "endTime": 15.0,
    "text": "Oh, I, uh..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 15.0,
    "endTime": 17.0,
    "text": "I was just eating some, uh..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 17.0,
    "endTime": 20.0,
    "text": "What's that awful stuff that's like fruit that people decorate plates with?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 20.0,
    "endTime": 22.0,
    "text": "You mean a vegetable?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 22.0,
    "endTime": 23.0,
    "text": "Uh, yes."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 23.0,
    "endTime": 26.0,
    "text": "That's what stained my lips: a verjitul."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 26.0,
    "endTime": 26.0,
    "text": "What kind?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 27.0,
    "endTime": 28.0,
    "text": "A red... a red one?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 28.0,
    "endTime": 29.0,
    "text": "Okay, stop lying."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 30.0,
    "endTime": 30.0,
    "text": "We saw her."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 30.0,
    "endTime": 31.0,
    "text": "Who is she?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 31.0,
    "endTime": 34.0,
    "text": "Uh, what's the name of those people that you pay to make your skin cry until you're thin?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 35.0,
    "endTime": 36.0,
    "text": "A personal trainer?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 36.0,
    "endTime": 36.0,
    "text": "That's it!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 36.0,
    "endTime": 40.0,
    "text": "She was reminding me I have to go to that place where the bicycles go nowhere."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 40.0,
    "endTime": 41.0,
    "text": "You mean the gym?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 41.0,
    "endTime": 41.0,
    "text": "Yes, the gym."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 42.0,
    "endTime": 42.0,
    "text": "And I'm late."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 42.0,
    "endTime": 43.0,
    "text": "Okay, bye!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 43.0,
    "endTime": 46.0,
    "text": "I don't think he's going to the gym."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 46.0,
    "endTime": 49.0,
    "text": "Because the only gym he goes to is Gym the Cashier at the donut store?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 49.0,
    "endTime": 54.0,
    "text": "No, I mean, yes, but also because that gym bag he grabbed was a woman's purse."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 58.0,
    "endTime": 60.0,
    "text": "Ooh, I'm going to the gym."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 60.0,
    "endTime": 61.0,
    "text": "Liar!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 61.0,
    "endTime": 62.0,
    "text": "He's buying perfume for that woman."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 63.0,
    "endTime": 64.0,
    "text": "Maybe it's just for him."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 64.0,
    "endTime": 66.0,
    "text": "Yeah, sure, to hide the scent of his shame!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 66.0,
    "endTime": 66.0,
    "text": "Shame!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 66.0,
    "endTime": 67.0,
    "text": "Ah!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 68.0,
    "endTime": 68.0,
    "text": "That was close."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 69.0,
    "endTime": 70.0,
    "text": "He nearly saw..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 70.0,
    "endTime": 72.0,
    "text": "Huh?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 73.0,
    "endTime": 78.0,
    "text": "I guess 4K is how far you have to stand away from the camera so you don't look like a photo from a dermatology textbook."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 78.0,
    "endTime": 80.0,
    "text": "Where did he go?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 84.0,
    "endTime": 85.0,
    "text": "Huh?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 85.0,
    "endTime": 85.0,
    "text": "Huh?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 89.0,
    "endTime": 103.0,
    "text": "Look!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 103.0,
    "endTime": 104.0,
    "text": "It's the lady we saw at home!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 105.0,
    "endTime": 107.0,
    "text": "Well, hello, girls."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 108.0,
    "endTime": 109.0,
    "text": "Let's eavesdrop."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 110.0,
    "endTime": 111.0,
    "text": "Ah, Samantha, finally."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 111.0,
    "endTime": 114.0,
    "text": "We've been waiting so long, Angela's clothes are back in fashion."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 115.0,
    "endTime": 117.0,
    "text": "Better late than ugly, Maria."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 117.0,
    "endTime": 120.0,
    "text": "A girl needs to make some effort for her man."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 120.0,
    "endTime": 123.0,
    "text": "Samantha, darling, the last time you were a girl, men still had gills."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 124.0,
    "endTime": 128.0,
    "text": "So, when do we get to meet this elusive boyfriend of yours?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 128.0,
    "endTime": 130.0,
    "text": "Oh, he's not elusive, Angela."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 130.0,
    "endTime": 134.0,
    "text": "He just doesn't like to answer questions straightforwardly and prefers changing the subject to avoid them."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 135.0,
    "endTime": 138.0,
    "text": "Samantha, are you nervous because we might judge your new boyfriend?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 138.0,
    "endTime": 142.0,
    "text": "No, Violet, she's worried about how mimes place their orders at the drive-thru."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 143.0,
    "endTime": 145.0,
    "text": "Ah, you younger women are so demanding."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 145.0,
    "endTime": 148.0,
    "text": "So what if Samantha's boyfriend isn't around that much?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 148.0,
    "endTime": 151.0,
    "text": "As long as a man has a pulse and a smile, who cares?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 151.0,
    "endTime": 153.0,
    "text": "I'd be so happy to get a man with either of those things."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 153.0,
    "endTime": 155.0,
    "text": "And at my age, I don't care which."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 156.0,
    "endTime": 158.0,
    "text": "Do you think he might have a friend for me?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 158.0,
    "endTime": 160.0,
    "text": "Yes, Violet, the Easter Bunny."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 160.0,
    "endTime": 162.0,
    "text": "Now, you listen here."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 162.0,
    "endTime": 163.0,
    "text": "My man does exist."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 163.0,
    "endTime": 166.0,
    "text": "As a matter of fact, I'm meeting him in the park later."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 166.0,
    "endTime": 167.0,
    "text": "What the what?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 169.0,
    "endTime": 174.0,
    "text": "Ah, this is taking forever."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 174.0,
    "endTime": 175.0,
    "text": "I've not got a lot of time."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 175.0,
    "endTime": 177.0,
    "text": "Skin and regrets, yes, but time, no."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 177.0,
    "endTime": 179.0,
    "text": "Do you think maybe he's running a little late?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 180.0,
    "endTime": 181.0,
    "text": "No, Violet, he arrived on time."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 181.0,
    "endTime": 183.0,
    "text": "He just set our watches early for a prank."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 185.0,
    "endTime": 190.0,
    "text": "Oh, there he is."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 190.0,
    "endTime": 191.0,
    "text": "Hello, sugar."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 192.0,
    "endTime": 193.0,
    "text": "Hey, honey."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 193.0,
    "endTime": 195.0,
    "text": "How's your day been?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 197.0,
    "endTime": 203.0,
    "text": "Oh, it makes my heart skip a beat to know that love can still blossom at our age."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 204.0,
    "endTime": 206.0,
    "text": "Wait, that's two beats."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 206.0,
    "endTime": 206.0,
    "text": "Three."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 207.0,
    "endTime": 208.0,
    "text": "Somebody do something."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 208.0,
    "endTime": 209.0,
    "text": "Oh, yeah, there it is."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 210.0,
    "endTime": 213.0,
    "text": "I can't believe it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 213.0,
    "endTime": 218.0,
    "text": "Dad always said Mom was out of his league, but I never thought he'd want to get back down into his own league."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 219.0,
    "endTime": 220.0,
    "text": "What's that?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 221.0,
    "endTime": 222.0,
    "text": "A bombshell that just got dropped on us."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 222.0,
    "endTime": 223.0,
    "text": "Huh."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 223.0,
    "endTime": 224.0,
    "text": "Always thought that was a metaphor."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 228.0,
    "endTime": 231.0,
    "text": "We know about Samantha."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 231.0,
    "endTime": 232.0,
    "text": "Oh."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 232.0,
    "endTime": 236.0,
    "text": "Well, I guess you're bound to find out one day."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 236.0,
    "endTime": 237.0,
    "text": "How do you feel about it?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 238.0,
    "endTime": 239.0,
    "text": "Oh, just great."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 239.0,
    "endTime": 241.0,
    "text": "How do you think Mom would feel about it?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 241.0,
    "endTime": 243.0,
    "text": "Well, she's not around in the day."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 243.0,
    "endTime": 245.0,
    "text": "I've got to find some way of keeping myself entertained."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 246.0,
    "endTime": 247.0,
    "text": "Entertained?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 248.0,
    "endTime": 250.0,
    "text": "Is it so bad that I have some fun?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 250.0,
    "endTime": 252.0,
    "text": "I enjoy the time I spend with my girls."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 252.0,
    "endTime": 253.0,
    "text": "Girls!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 253.0,
    "endTime": 253.0,
    "text": "Plural!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 254.0,
    "endTime": 257.0,
    "text": "What difference does it make if it's more than one?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 257.0,
    "endTime": 258.0,
    "text": "You maggot."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 259.0,
    "endTime": 259.0,
    "text": "How many?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 259.0,
    "endTime": 262.0,
    "text": "Three at the moment, but you know, the more the merrier."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 262.0,
    "endTime": 263.0,
    "text": "I think I'm going to be sick."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 264.0,
    "endTime": 266.0,
    "text": "Our dad has a secret double life."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 266.0,
    "endTime": 268.0,
    "text": "Darwin, smash another plate."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 269.0,
    "endTime": 270.0,
    "text": "Hold on."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 286.0,
    "endTime": 286.0,
    "text": "Dad, nab it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 287.0,
    "endTime": 288.0,
    "text": " I bought the paper ones."
  }
]